00:18:47,501 --> 00:18:51,213
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, my father-in-law is Pissmaster,
so why don't you ask him?</font>

335
00:18:51,297 --> 00:18:55,926
<font face="Serif" size="18">What the--? Rick Sanchez, the Pissmaster?
Okay, this is not a good look.</font>

336
00:18:56,010 --> 00:19:00,264
<font face="Serif" size="18">This family, man. Look,
I don't know what weird shit you two are pulling,</font>

337
00:19:00,348 --> 00:19:03,142
<font face="Serif" size="18">but it's completely unstick worthy.
We're done here.</font>

338
00:19:03,225 --> 00:19:04,393
<font face="Serif" size="18">But I didn't know.</font>

339
00:19:04,477 --> 00:19:05,686
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm a good guy.</font>

340
00:19:05,770 --> 00:19:07,647
<font face="Serif" size="18">I made you all famous.</font>

341
00:19:07,730 --> 00:19:09,273
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm a thousand years old.</font>

342
00:19:09,357 --> 00:19:11,901
<font face="Serif" size="18">You know how many Flamingo Dads I've seen?</font>

343
00:19:11,984 --> 00:19:13,361
<font face="Serif" size="18">Don't orb us.</font>

344
00:19:15,780 --> 00:19:18,949
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't get it.
You were Pissmaster the whole time?</font>

345
00:19:19,033 --> 00:19:20,326
<font face="Serif" size="18">Obviously not, Jerry.</font>

346
00:19:20,409 --> 00:19:24,246
<font face="Serif" size="18">I put the suit on once Pissmaster kill--
Uh, when you made him--</font>

347
00:19:25,456 --> 00:19:28,918
<font face="Serif" size="18">Um, yeah, I've always been Pissmaster.</font>

348
00:19:29,001 --> 00:19:34,674
<font face="Serif" size="18">But that would mean you let my dad beat you up
just so he could, like, feel more confident?</font>

349
00:19:34,757 --> 00:19:36,425
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Damn, Rick.
- That's amazing.</font>

350
00:19:36,509 --> 00:19:41,222
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hold on, what?--? Everyone's just accepting this?
Wait, wasn't Pissmaster an alien?</font>

351
00:19:41,305 --> 00:19:43,182
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Probably a robot.
- He obviously <i>Avatar'd</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> it.</font>

352
00:19:43,265 --> 00:19:45,434
<font face="Serif" size="18">But why?
Why would Rick even prop me up like that?</font>

353
00:19:45,518 --> 00:19:50,064
<font face="Serif" size="18">Jesus, Jerry. Rick did something nice
for once, okay? He's trying to change.</font>

354
00:19:52,650 --> 00:19:55,194
<font face="Serif" size="18">[ship] <i>You are no longer worthy of Mitsubishi.</i></font>

355
00:19:56,946 --> 00:20:00,616
<font face="Serif" size="18">Proud of you, Dad.
Or should I say, Pissmaster.</font>

356
00:20:00,700 --> 00:20:02,952
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah. Grandpa, sorry I yelled at you.</font>

357
00:20:03,035 --> 00:20:07,415
<font face="Serif" size="18">And sorry for trying to stop you
from killing yourself with a nuclear bomb.</font>

358
00:20:07,498 --> 00:20:10,251
<font face="Serif" size="18">I just really liked having an orb.</font>

359
00:20:10,334 --> 00:20:11,544
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ah, don't sweat it, Jer.</font>

360
00:20:11,627 --> 00:20:12,962
<font face="Serif" size="18">Piss under the bridge.</font>

361
00:20:13,879 --> 00:20:15,756
<font face="Serif" size="18">Man, I guess the therapy worked, huh?</font>

362
00:20:15,840 --> 00:20:18,259
<font face="Serif" size="18">Opening up,
doing all that just to make my dad feel good.</font>

363
00:20:18,342 --> 00:20:22,346
<font face="Serif" size="18">- That's pretty great of you, Rick.
- Yeah. That's right, Morty. That's right.</font>

364
00:20:22,430 --> 00:20:26,058
<font face="Serif" size="18">You have to promise not to tell anyone,
but your dad made Pissmaster kill himself.</font>

365
00:20:26,142 --> 00:20:28,269
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Oh, man, what?
- Yeah, I mean, I found him dead</font>

366
00:20:28,352 --> 00:20:31,981
<font face="Serif" size="18">and I put on his suit.
But look at this. He literally blames your dad.</font>

367
00:20:32,064 --> 00:20:36,610
<font face="Serif" size="18">Holy shit. Wait, you kept the suicide note?
That's so messed up.</font>

368
00:20:36,694 --> 00:20:39,447
<font face="Serif" size="18">I know. I had to tell someone, Morty.
I couldn't just sit on that.</font>

369
00:20:39,530 --> 00:20:42,032
<font face="Serif" size="18">- And you expect me to?
- Morty, no, what are you doing?</font>

370
00:20:42,491 --> 00:20:43,659
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Jerry screams]</font>

371
00:20:43,743 --> 00:20:47,037
<font face="Serif" size="18">- What the hell? He killed himself?
- Jesus, Dad, you should've told us.</font>

372
00:20:47,121 --> 00:20:49,498
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Especially if Jerry murdered him.
- Wait, don't say that.</font>

373
00:20:49,582 --> 00:20:51,375
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I didn't murder.
- I thought it was cool</font>

374
00:20:51,459 --> 00:20:53,586
<font face="Serif" size="18">- that I withheld that information.
- But you didn't.</font>

375
00:20:53,669 --> 00:20:57,465
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You're walking around with the note.
- Gotta keep it in your heart as a great sacrifice.</font>

376
00:20:57,548 --> 00:21:01,093
<font face="Serif" size="18">- That's the cool move.
- How am I the bad guy? He sprayed piss on us.</font>

377
00:21:01,177 --> 00:21:03,387
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You all cheered me on.
- Don't drag us into this.</font>

378
00:21:03,471 --> 00:21:05,389
<font face="Serif" size="18">Again, I told you this would happen.</font>

379
00:21:05,473 --> 00:21:06,932
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Oh, get off your high horse.
- Boo.</font>

380
00:21:07,016 --> 00:21:09,268
<font face="Serif" size="18">Go ahead and boo.
I was breathing piss. Think I care?</font>

381
00:21:09,351 --> 00:21:10,978
<font face="Serif" size="18">Is this what it's like to trend?</font>

382
00:21:11,061 --> 00:21:14,940
<font face="Serif" size="18">This is a nightmare.
I should've just let him pee on my daughter.</font>

383
00:21:15,024 --> 00:21:16,233
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Summer] What the hell, Dad?</font>

384
00:21:16,609 --> 00:21:18,027
<font face="Serif" size="18">[theme music playing]</font>

385
00:21:48,390 --> 00:21:53,020
<font face="Serif" size="18">How about Jack Miller, aka carjack?
He lifted a car off a stranger.</font>

386
00:21:53,103 --> 00:21:54,063
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I guess.
- Next.</font>

387
00:21:54,146 --> 00:21:56,857
<font face="Serif" size="18">Orb-no. We're fresh off a dad and a piss guy.</font>

388
00:21:56,941 --> 00:22:01,362
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Maybe we add someone that's already powerful?
- We have to be realistic about who we can get.</font>

389
00:22:01,445 --> 00:22:04,240
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I have a pitch.
- We're not going to add Scarlett Johansson.</font>

390
00:22:04,323 --> 00:22:10,704
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Next up, Mr. Nimbus. Lord of the oceans.
- Oh, I hear he controls the police.</font>

391
00:22:10,788 --> 00:22:12,581
<font face="Serif" size="18">- The police?
- [all] Orb-yes.</font>

392
00:22:12,665 --> 00:22:16,126
<font face="Serif" size="18">Guys, I already checked.
His reps say he's really busy right now.</font>

393
00:22:16,210 --> 00:22:18,754
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Everyone says that.
- Oh, and we're not busy?</font>

